from vanderby david vanderbyl subject re a question about outlet wire olsen write i notice at the fusebox that some circuit have the with grind and that on these circuit the grind wire wa tie to the same bu a the neutral white wire thi be contrary to the electrical code and should be fix sorry but thi be exactly accord to the nec no need to be sorry i blow it on thi one at the main breaker box where there be a thick wire grind lead to the earth both neutral and grind be hook to thi bu in any other breaker box or an outlet box etc the grind and neutral must not be connect together 